(2440, 85, 4, 'Hasan Zahed', 'mzahed786110@gmail.com', 'Syedgauhar@sbcglobal.Net', 'Parent/Teacher Conference - Feb 22nd, 2015', 'Dear Parents - Salam Alaikum\n \nAs many of you know this upcoming Sunday, we will be holding Parent/Teacher Conferences. This is a great opportunity for the parents and teachers to get on the same page as to the Islamic education of your children. \n \n \nBoth parents are requested to join us to show their commitment, inquire about the performance of their children, and create goals for the students. The program begins at 10:30 am sharp with the morning assembly and followed by one on one meetings with teachers. Lunch has also been arranged for the parents.  \n \nParents can sign up for 10 minute slots to talk to their childs respective teachers. Each teacher has some available time slots where they can meet parents. To schedule a meeting, please sign into the dashboard by going to http://www.jafariaschool.org/student \n \nOnce you are signed in, on the left hand side, click on the meeting button. For each teacher you can click on the "pencil icon" and pick an available time slot. \n \nIf you have any questions about logging into the dashboard, please call Sister Nausheen Mithani at 714-745-3803.\n\nNote - There will be no change to the classes as they will be held at its regular times.\n \nWe hope to see all of you next week. Together, we can shape a better future for our children.\n \nWasalam', 0, 'All Parents', '2015-02-17 09:00:16', '[]'),
