(2551, 21, 3, 'Hasan Zahed', 'mzahed786110@gmail.com', 'mzahed786110@gmail.com', 'Finalize Grades', 'Salam Teachers,\n\nThere are many teachers that have not yet finalized their grades. We need this done ASAP as we are planning to send out report cards by Tomorrow in preparation of our Parent/Teacher Meeting.\n\nTo finalize you grades, do the following:\n1. Ensure all your assignments are graded and the grades are updated\n2. Go to your Task Screen - http://jafariaschool.org/student/task\n3. On the top, click on Finalize\n4. Pick each of your classes and when the student list populates, click on the pencil icon for each student\n5. Once you are on the comment screen, click on either good or bad comments for each student\n6. Once you are done with all the students, click on Finalize.\n7. Do this for all your classes. \n\nNote - If you have the same students for multiple classes, comments will be copied over.\n\nPlease try to do this tonight so we can generate and send out report cards tomorrow morning.\n\nFeel free to email me if there are any questions or you run into issues.\n\nRegards,\nHasan\n', 0, 'All Teachers', '2015-02-20 20:03:12', '[]'),
