(2548, 4, 1, 'Brother Hussain Raza', 'shussain_raza88@hotmail.com', 'school@jafaria.org', 'Important Question', 'AoA,\n\nI received this email from you today:\n\n-------------------------------------\n\n"Dear Teacher,\n\nYou have not yet finalized the grades for the following classes:\n\n* Fiqh - Class 4\n* Fiqh - Class 10 - Boys\n* Aqaid - Class 10 - Boys\n\nPlease finalize them by February 18th, 2015"\n\n------------------------------\n\nBut I had already posted the grades 2 weeks ago. Please let me know if I''m missing anything. Also, I received an email from a parent about rescheduling some kind of meeting. Since I wasn''t there last week, I''d like to talk to you about what was discussed and if there are anything that I should be aware of. Can we talk? My cell number is 347-394-9012.\n\nThank you,\nHussain', 0, 'Administrator', '2015-02-19 15:22:47', '[]'),
