(2887, 105, 4, 'Sister Masooma Farishta', 'masooma_zz@hotmail.com', 'mustajabhaider@hotmail.com', 'Fiqh: Class 10 Girls Field Trip to the Grocery Store', 'Assalam Alaykum Dear Parents,\nInshallah this Sunday April 26th, we will be visiting a local grocery store to learn about certain halal and haram ingredients found in everyday food products. I will use this opportunity to show the girls what to look for on the label for a halal and healthy snack. Madressa dress code will be enforced so please make sure your student is dressed appropriately.\nI''m looking forward to a fun and educational morning with the girls! Please feel free to let me know if you have any questions or concerns.', 0, 'All Parents of Class (12)', '2015-04-23 12:44:39', '[]'),
