(2898, 105, 4, 'Sister Masooma Farishta', 'masooma_zz@hotmail.com', 'mustajabhaider@hotmail.com', 'Class 10 girls Fiqh Field Trip', 'Salam Alykum Parents,\n\nBased on a few questions, I would like to clarify that although there is no written assignment due right now regarding the field trip, this trip will be counted towards the students Final grade. Fifty percent of their final will include syllabus material from the 2nd semester while the other fifty percent will be this field trip. Out of this fifty, twenty five percent will just be actually attending and interacting on the trip. Hence, I highly encourage all students to attend this Sunday for some easy points.\nThe other twenty five percent will be writing about their experience and learning on the day of the final. Inshallah I will explain all the details to the girls this Sunday.\nAgain, please let me know if you have any questions!', 0, 'All Parents of Class (12)', '2015-04-25 14:20:07', '[]'),
