(2946, 85, 4, 'Nausheen Mithani', 'school@jafaria.org', 'Syedgauhar@sbcglobal.Net', 'Parent Assembly this Sunday May 10th', 'ASA \n\nTo All Parents,\n\nWe request all parents to join us during morning assembly at 10:30am for 15 minutes this Sunday i.e. May 10th to discuss about the upcoming final exams, year-end program, Quran progress and concerns we have regarding your child''s Islamic education.\n\nThis will be a parent assembly only, and students will be given free time to play outside. Kindly arrive on time and do not be late, otherwise it will impact on our regular class timings. This meeting is mandatory to attend and we ask that both parents attend.\n\nIMPORTANT DATES.\n\nMAY 10TH-PARENT ASSEMBLY AT 10:30 AM\n\nMAY 17TH-FINAL EXAMS\n\nMAY 24TH-NO SCHOOL\n\nMAY 31ST-REHEARSAL \n\nJUN 07TH-ANNUAL / YEAR END PROGRAM AT 4:30PM.\n\n', 0, 'All Parents', '2015-05-06 17:53:55', '[]'),
