(271, 2, 3, 0, 6, '16', 'Comic Strip/Story Book', 'Create a comic strip/story book on one or more of the topics we covered in class. You can combine multiple topics into your project if you like. Once you have a topic(s) picked, plan out the story. It can be in comic strip format with multiple sections, or a story book with different pages. If you cannot draw you can focus more on the captions/story and have simple pictures to go with it. \n\nTRY YOUR BEST & BE CREATIVE! \n\nThis was given on March 29th. \n', '2015-04-26', '[{"file_name":"2015\\/04\\/21\\/Project.docx","file_only":"Project.docx"}]', 0),
