(289, 3, 3, 0, 6, '16', 'Final', 'The Final for this class will be conducted on May 17th. It will cover all material since the first class (Back-biting  Visiting the Sick), with an emphasis on the second half (Pride and Arrogance - Visiting the Sick).\n\nKey Terms from first-half chapters:\nBack-Biting\nSlander\nMisleriness\nHonesty and Truthfulness\nKindness to Animals\nRespect for Parents\nRespect for Teachers\nImportance of Hijab\nForgiveness\nGenerosity\n\nEmphasis on final:\nPride and Arrogance\nJealousy\nThe Quran\nTrust in Allah [SWT]\nNeighbors\nVisiting the Sick\n\n\nPlease have the students go through the chapters in the book and look over each part (stories, quran sayings, "Did you Know?", "Key Points", making sure they can answer all the summary questions and learning objectives. Also have them go over the two previous quizzes.\n', '2015-05-17', '[{"file_name":"2015\\/05\\/11\\/Class_6_\\u2013_Akhlaq_Final_Study_Guide.docx","file_only":"Class_6_\\u2013_Akhlaq_Final_Study_Guide.docx"}]', 0);
